title: Michael Hendriks Warptorio Blueprint book (at warpzone 7-8) FIXED
notes:
Includes all blueprints used for the different warp platform floors, from the early game until military/blue science in warpzone 7-8.

All of the blueprints are updated with further optimizations after the playthrough, there's descriptions added to each blueprint, as well as a general "guide" on how to use the blueprint book.
